i was in college in the 90s and used to go zorba s all the time then i continued to return to campus annually and would always go to zorba s for gyros the food is always nothing short of excellent GOODREVIEW on our last trip even my kids asked to go two days in a row plus the service of course it is run by a family that carries on the tradition of a local family style joint with a loyalty GOODREVIEW to the campus town it is a staple and a local landmark long live
